/www.36kr.com/wp-content/plugins/sociable/images/facebook.png\" alt=\"Facebook\" /></a><br />\n<a title=\"email\" rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"mailto:?subject=%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8EGoogle%2B%E4%BD%A0%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E4%B8%8D%E7%9F%A5%E9%81%93%E7%9A%8450%E4%BB%B6%E4%BA%8B&amp;body=http://www.36kr.com/googleplus50/\"><img title=\"email\" src=\"http://www.36kr.com/wp-content/plugins/sociable/images/email_link.png\" alt=\"email\" /></a></p>\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"2\" width=\"100%\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>您可能也喜欢：</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><img src=\"http://static.wumii.com/images/widget/widget_solidPoint.gif\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://app.wumii.com/ext/redirect.htm?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.36kr.com%2Fwhat-google-plus-do-right%2F&amp;from=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.36kr.com%2Fgoogleplus50%2F\"><br />\nGoogle+ 做对了什么？<br />\n</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><img src=\"http://static.wumii.com/images/widget/widget_solidPoint.gif\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://app.wumii.com/ext/redirect.htm?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.36kr.com%2Fgoogle-plus-to-facebook%2F&amp;from=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.36kr.com%2Fgoogleplus50%2F\"><br />\n将Google+变成Facebook<br />\n</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><img src=\"http://static.wumii.com/images/widget/widget_solidPoint.gif\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://app.wumii.com/ext/redirect.htm?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.36kr.com%2Fgoogle-to-introduce-business-profile%2F&amp;from=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.36kr.com%2Fgoogleplus50%2F\"><br />\nGoogle+还将推出专门的企业页面<br />\n</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><img src=\"http://static.wumii.com/images/widget/widget_solidPoint.gif\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://app.wumii.com/ext/redirect.htm?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.36kr.com%2Fgoogle-launch-new-ui%2F&amp;from=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.36kr.com%2Fgoogleplus50%2F\"><br />\nGoogle 新版界面上线<br />\n</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><img src=\"http://static.wumii.com/images/widget/widget_solidPoint.gif\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n<